{"tid":1685851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕節國際文宣]：基督徒組團「十字架苦行」，十字架上面寫晒貼晒香港慘況同文宣","createTime":"2019-10-31T19:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T19:30:24.000Z","uid":273116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d49b7c0adf2600f61fd37449269f551eb601f6b","tid":1685851,"uid":273116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Feel到Popo好緊火 想射又無得射<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個同sing hallelujah to the lord一樣射咗會有手尾</blockquote>萬聖節班基督徒唔出得黎慶祝<br />\n留名等聖誕節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>除咗報佳音，大嗌：「聖誕快樂！耶穌愛你！」之外，忽然諗到聖誕節基督徒可以組團<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一齊背大大個<span style=\"color: red;\">十字架</span>苦行，個十字架上面寫晒貼晒香港人嘅慘況<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">文宣</span>之類。</span><br />\n<blockquote>推自己開個post 叫人幫手推一推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我開咗呢個post。<br />\n<br />\n雖然復活節啱topic啲，但最近嘅節日就係聖誕節。呢個剩係一個idea嚟。唔知會唔會真係有人做⋯⋯"},{"pid":"b0b71e5a8e76e398c682b19adbd7adcbd1ade235","tid":1685851,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:56:01.000Z","msg":"我睇到IG有個post講基督徒使命<br />\n我覺得佢講得好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4PQXEUhq_p/?igshid=iryyqo7ykpty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4PQXEUhq_p%2F%3Figshid%3Diryyqo7ykpty&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=87399c19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4PQXEUhq_p%2F%3Figshid%3Diryyqo7ykpty&h=d81fdfe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4PQXEUhq_p/?igshid=iryyqo7ykpty</a>"},{"pid":"c8843f6db7ef9f224a65160b6f3d3d4ccf6307c6","tid":1685851,"uid":273116,"like":1,"disli